sources.title: Gossip Nation | Full Drama Movie | Ejike Asiegbu | Aileen Beale | Nollywood
sources.description:
Gossip Nation - Blacktown, in Sydney's West, is the home to a growing African community. Jealousy and tragedy haunt the characters as their lives are tainted with gossip but always hold hope for redemption, forgiveness, and understanding.
2012.  Stars: Ejike Asiegbu, Aileen Beale, Taryn Brine

metadata.Plot: In the year 2000, a new wave of African immigrants and refugees arrived on the shores of Australia. Many migrated to a small suburb in the west of Sydney called 'Blacktown'. As the African community grew, racial and cultural tensions arose.
metadata.Actors: Ejike Asiegbu, Aileen Beale, Taryn Brine
